To turn on this free service, the repo owner would need to do steps 1 and 2 of https://docs.travis-ci.com/user/getting-started/

wip: fixes #14: parser for kubectl command line

Parser holds the syntax tree of the command line. The class is used to
read the json schema into a tree structure. The class is also used to
identify the tokens in a command line by walking the tree and returning
a sequence of possible suggestions at any given node in the walk
